result.name: ANA Sushi

reviews.text: Very good eating and prompt service in Yoho Mall1, Yuen Long, Hongkong..

Took my aunt and uncle here for lunch, he walks with a slight limp and the staff was patient even when we were impeding their ability to get by.  Onto the food, the donburi/chirashi bowls are enough to satisfy an adult. The sashimi was fresh and each slice was well portioned.  They we're busy and well staffed but it took 2 reminders to get the check but otherwise food was delicious.

Japanese restaurant serving nice and fresh food, the sushi was very good, it came with appetizer, salad and dessert. Also had chicken filet with udon good and well seasoned. Staff were ok not very attentive but doing the work. The price is a bit expensive considering the portions. Between this restaurant and senju sushi from the same group of restaurant I prefer senju. (More attentive staff and tastier food.)

Expensive Japanese food. Poor service. We waited for 30 minutes before checking in and realizing that the order was never put into the system by the waitress. Had to always ask for a tea refill because the staff was not attentive.
Very good food and service!

result.name: YOHO MALL I

reviews.text: A clean, well organised mall with more stores than you can imagine. Well maintained and hygienic restrooms as frequently spaced and the proximity to the MTR is a big plus!

Huge variety! It's great for shopping and dining 👍 they also have a cinema, for entertainment, showing a variety of Western and Asian movies. Pop-up stalls and exhibitions are constantly visiting the mall giving shoppers something interesting to do while walking from shop to shop, or just to celebrate the current events (popular movies, holidays, brands etc.)

Nothing special different from other plaza
It’s crowded. Many mainland people surrounded. 
Although it’s so many restaurant, you need to queue for the restaurant was extremely long.
And the price is not reasonable.
Very disappointed. 
Not recommend.
a grand n morden mall with variaties of dinning places, great to visit...

Many restaurants & cafe, you can find any kind of food & style, this should be the biggest shopping mall at Yuen Long area at moment, very convenient and easy to access, just a min. walk linked with West Rail Yuen Long station.

reviews.text: 座位舒適環境佳, 星期一至五有午市套餐由$158起。晚市没有套餐價錢貴, 物非所值

食物質素不錯
不過價錢頗貴，CP 值唔多高
服務態度極好吧台的廚師只要你願意就會跟你聊天食物質素極好
食物很好吃和服務態度都幾好！
繁忙時段，不建議取大枱票(6-8人)。本身是5個大人和1個2歲小朋友，但因為此餐廳欠缺彈性，不合拼餐枱，最後我們等了一小時，最後19：02入座。
